三、教學目標 Objectives


本課程首先介紹審計市場實證研究總論、研究方法論、審計市場研究基礎理論等三大基礎課程，奠下學生進入審計研究領域的基礎後，再針對公司治理、盈餘管理、審計品質、與稅務處理態度等理論與實務均重要的議題，進行深入研討。希望透過本課程的內容，使修課學生可以由學術研究的角度，瞭解資本市場中財報資訊品質與審計功能的重要性。 


This course is a survey of recent empirical research in auditing.  The primary purpose of this course is to introduce a significant number of the research questions and methods in empirical research in auditing.  The assigned readings, classroom discussions, term-paper, and final exam are designed for that purpose. The specific course objectives are: (1) to develop the skills to read and critique accounting research; (2) to apply these skills to auditing research literature; and (3) to foster the ability to independently formulate academic research projects. 


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall Description一、審計市場實證研究議題二、實證研究方法論三、審計市場研究基礎理論四、盈餘品質之衡量五、審計品質之研究六、稅務治理


●分週敘述 Weekly Schedule





